name: The Magical Item #11: Machkal: The Deadly Coliseum
description: Dino reaches the 11th location, Mashkal, The Deadly Coliseum. The population here is known for the art of breeding fairies. To preserve the city's strength, all external fairies must complete a fighting test against the guardians. Only the strong can go through. As a foreigner, Dino is summoned to the arena #45 to battle guardian #5X. Jaru evolves into a Doggo Beast using the Time Power he earned in location #10. Against him is one of the most experienced fairies: Pyriado. This is a fierce battle that Dino and his crew cannot afford to lose. The whole world is watching through the eyes of The Magical beast TV. Unlocking this location will increase your Combat Attribute by 710 MPs.
